

1. Introduction :  we handles user information when you use our mobile application ("App"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. By using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

2. No Collection of Personal Data We do not collect, store, or process any personal information from users of the App. This means:

No personal data (such as name, email address, or phone number) is collected.
No usage data (such as browsing history, app interaction, or activity logs) is tracked.
No device information is gathered.
3. App Features Although we do not collect data, the App still offers its full range of functionalities, including:

Attendance tracking (locally on the device).
Media access for educational content (without cloud-based data storage).
Automated testing and quizzes (managed within the App itself, without external servers).
Parental oversight (managed within the family’s devices).
All features are handled locally within the app, and no information is transmitted or stored on our servers.

4. Data Security Since we do not collect or store data, there are no concerns about third-party access or data breaches related to your personal information. However, it is important for users to ensure their own devices are secure and protected from unauthorized access.

5. Children’s Privacy Our App is designed for use by teachers, students, and their parents. We do not collect personal data from children or any other users.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated through the App or via a notification.

